<span style="font-size: 18px; color: #7E57C2;"><b>Controls :</b></span><br>

 Each of the four players has its own control menu<br><br>
<span style="color: #5E35B1;">●</span> Open menu : hold your finger (or left mouse button) for more than one second on the desired player<br>
<span style="color: #5E35B1;">●</span> Full‑screen mode : double‑click (works only in landscape orientation)<br>
<span style="color: #5E35B1;">●</span> Zoom : standard zoom gestures (with fingers) or mouse wheel<br><br>

